American Telephone andTelegraph Co said small businesses can win up to a 10 pctdiscount on telephone equipment under a new program.    According to the America's Choice Bonus Program, customersthat rent certain phone systems can earn credits each time theypay their monthly or fixed term lease bills.    The credits can be used in the purchase of ATT products,including communications systems and the System 25 PBX, atelephone switch for voice and data communications. Customerswill receive a 50 dlrs initial credit, and additions to theiraccount equivalent to 10 pct of their rental payments. Reuter&#3;